+- **Z-Index**: Focus Mode uses `z-[100]`, onboarding uses `z-50` (already correct)
+- **Layering**: Focus Mode overlay sits above onboarding overlay
+- **Close Behavior**: Closing Focus Mode returns to onboarding (already working)
